steps.name: BASE - Typing visible textbox by setValue function with value "jitapicol007bdatetime" and needClickOption is "true"
BASE - Check list elmenet has visible element by locator:
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I create new group API with name "groupapi007b"
Then I should see group api "groupapi007b" displayed in api list
When I select api name "groupapi007b" from list
When I add new API endpoint
When I set dropdown label "Method Type" in modal popup to value "GET"
When I set textbox label "URL" in modal popup to value "/v1/jitera/datetime"
When I set textbox label "Name" in modal popup to value "jitera"
When I set dropdown label "Action" in modal popup to value "Search"
When I set dropdown label "Model" in modal popup to value "jitapi007bs"
When I press general button "Create" in modal popup
Then I should see method "GET" with endpoint "/v1/jitera/datetime" displayed
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/v1/jitera/datetime"
When I click tab "SQL Query" in floating panel
When I add row Query index "1" with static value - value "OR","jitapi007bs.jitapicol007bdate","Equal To","static value","Today"
When I add row Query index "2" with static value - value "OR","jitapi007bs.jitapicol007bdatetime","Equal To","static value","Now"
When I close the floating panel
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "groupapi007b" from list
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/v1/jitera/datetime"
When I click tab "SQL Query" in floating panel
Then I should see floating panel has Model with static value - Query Table - row "1" - value "OR","jitapi007bs.jitapicol007bdate","Equal To","static value","Today"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with static value - Query Table - row "2" - value "OR","jitapi007bs.jitapicol007bdatetime","Equal To","static value","Now"
When I close the floating panel
When I delete API method "GET" with endpoint "/v1/jitera/datetime"
Then I should NOT see method "GET" with endpoint "/v1/jitera/datetime" displayed
